title: Biden attacks China and Russia for missing COP26
content: The US president calls the Chinese leader's absence from the Glasgow summit a "big mistake".

content: The Global Methane Pledge aims to cut methane emissions by 30% by 2030, compared with 2020 levels.

content: Sepp Blatter and Michel Platini, former world and European football heads, are charged with fraud.

content: Around 1,000 people had gathered at the venue in Sweden before a person fell and hit two others.
